<br>
Peaches said:<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>This Apostolic Tradition looks like putting to much faith and trust in man. And it makes Christianity sound too much like any other world religion. I don't put my faith and trust in man, I put my faith and trust in an all powerful God who is fully capable of revealing Himself to us and revealing His word to us.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
